name: Stars & Restraints Pullover Hoodie
description:
The most thought provoking image you will ever wear. Now available on a super comfy pullover hoodie. Interpret the meaning for yourself - some see the Stars & Restraints as a 3000 mile prison cell, however the true meaning is about how if you don't know your rights in this country, you lose them. 

Printed on soft 80% cotton/20% polyester black unisex pullover hoodie.
Has large front pocket and logo on sleeve. Minor imperfections with print can occur around pockets and seams.
